text: Star Channel is an Polish pay television channel owned by TVN Warner Bros. Discovery. The channel originally launched as the Polish version of Discovery Home & Health on 6 April 2011 and started broadcasting in 16:9 aspect ratio on 21 September 2014. On 4 December 2023, TVN Warner Bros. Discovery announced that the Polish version of Discovery Home & Health would be rebranded as Star Channel on 12 April 2024. == Logos == file:Discovery H&H.png;|6 April 2011-12 April 2024 file:Star Channel 2023.svg|12 April 2024-present Category:Television channels in Europe
